<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Renovata — Vasos que Vivem</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --moss: #2D4A2F;
    --moss-light: #3d6340;
    --cream: #F8F4EE;
    --cream-dark: #EDE8DF;
    --terra: #C47A3A;
    --green-soft: #7EB87A;
    --charcoal: #1C1C1A;
    --muted: #6B6B67;
    --white: #ffffff;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.2rem 5vw;
    background: rgba(248, 244, 238, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45, 74, 47, 0.12);
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--moss);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .logo span {
    color: var(--terra);
  }

  nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  nav ul a {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  nav ul a:hover { color: var(--moss); }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream) !important;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 500 !important;
    transition: background 0.2s !important;
  }

  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--moss-light) !important; color: var(--cream) !important; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-text {
    padding: 8vh 5vw 8vh 8vw;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--terra);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--moss);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terra);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 420px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--moss-light);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .btn-text {
    color: var(--moss);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-text:hover { gap: 0.7rem; }
  .btn-text::after { content: '→'; }

  .hero-visual {
    height: 100vh;
    background: var(--moss);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-svg-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-bg-circle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 70%;
    height: 70%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(126, 184, 122, 0.12);
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.08); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    right: 2.5rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(248, 244, 238, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* SECTION SHARED */
  section { padding: 7rem 8vw; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--moss);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* MANIFESTO */
  .manifesto {
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 7rem 12vw;
  }

  .manifesto-quote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--cream);
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }

  .manifesto-quote em {
    color: var(--green-soft);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .manifesto-sub {
    color: rgba(248,244,238,0.55);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  /* PRODUTOS */
  .produtos { background: var(--cream); }

  .produtos-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: end;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .produtos-intro p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .produtos-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .produto-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .produto-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(45, 74, 47, 0.12);
  }

  .produto-img {
    height: 260px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .produto-img-1 { background: #E8F0E8; }
  .produto-img-2 { background: #F0EAE0; }
  .produto-img-3 { background: #E0EAE8; }

  .produto-info {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .produto-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--terra);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .produto-nome {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .produto-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .produto-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .produto-preco {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--moss);
  }

  .produto-btn {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream);
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .produto-btn:hover { background: var(--moss-light); }

  /* DIFERENCIAIS */
  .diferenciais {
    background: var(--cream-dark);
  }

  .diferenciais-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  .diferencial {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-soft);
  }

  .diferencial-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .diferencial h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--moss);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .diferencial p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* PROCESSO */
  .processo { background: var(--cream); }

  .processo-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .processo-steps::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 28px;
    left: 10%;
    right: 10%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--cream-dark);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* DEPOIMENTOS */
  .depoimentos {
    background: var(--moss);
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .depoimentos .section-heading { color: var(--cream); }
  .depoimentos .section-label { color: var(--green-soft); }

  .depoimentos-intro {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: end;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .depoimentos-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .depoimento {
    background: rgba(248, 244, 238, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(248, 244, 238, 0.12);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .depoimento-stars {
    color: var(--terra);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .depoimento-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .depoimento-autor {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-soft);
  }

  .depoimento-local {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(248,244,238,0.4);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--cream-dark);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 8vw;
  }

  .cta-section .section-heading {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0.8rem auto 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: rgba(248,244,238,0.6);
    padding: 4rem 8vw 2rem;
  }

  .footer-top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(248,244,238,0.1);
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-logo span { color: var(--terra); }

  .footer-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 280px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-col h4 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }

  .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

  .footer-col ul a {
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(248,244,238,0.5);
    font-weight: 300;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .footer-col ul a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .hero-visual { height: 50vw; }
    .hero-text { padding: 6rem 6vw 3rem; }
    section { padding: 5rem 6vw; }
    .produtos-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .produtos-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .diferenciais-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .processo-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; row-gap: 2.5rem; }
    .processo-steps::before { display: none; }
    .depoimentos-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    nav ul { display: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .produtos-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .diferenciais-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .processo-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .fade-up {
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
  }

  .fade-up:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .fade-up:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

  @keyframes leafGrow {
    0% { transform: scale(0.5) rotate(-10deg); opacity: 0; }
    100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .leaf-anim {
    animation: leafGrow 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) 0.3s both;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a class="logo" href="#">Renovat<span>a</span></a>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#produtos">Produtos</a></li>
    <li><a href="#processo">Como funciona</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sobre">Sobre</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contato" class="nav-cta">Fale conosco</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow fade-up">Vasos Renováveis</p>
    <h1 class="fade-up">Plantar é<br/>um ato de<br/><em>renovação</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc fade-up">Vasos criados para crescer com suas plantas — e com você. Materiais renováveis, design atemporal, propósito claro.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions fade-up">
      <a href="#produtos" class="btn-primary">Ver coleção</a>
      <a href="#processo" class="btn-text">Como funciona</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="hero-bg-circle"></div>
    <div class="hero-svg-wrap">
      <svg class="leaf-anim" width="280" height="340" viewBox="0 0 280 340" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Vaso -->
        <rect x="90" y="240" width="100" height="80" rx="6" fill="#1A3B1C" opacity="0.7"/>
        <rect x="80" y="228" width="120" height="22" rx="4" fill="#1A3B1C" opacity="0.5"/>
        <!-- Terra -->
        <ellipse cx="140" cy="230" rx="54" ry="8" fill="#3d2910" opacity="0.6"/>
        <!-- Caule -->
        <path d="M140 228 C140 200 130 170 120 130 C110 90 128 50 140 20" stroke="#7EB87A" stroke-width="3.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
        <path d="M140 228 C140 200 150 170 160 130 C170 90 152 50 140 20" stroke="#5fa05a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" opacity="0.4"/>
        <!-- Folha grande esquerda -->
        <path d="M128 140 C100 120 68 110 60 85 C52 60 80 45 108 70 C124 84 130 120 128 140Z" fill="#7EB87A" opacity="0.9"/>
        <path d="M128 140 C115 115 95 100 80 78" stroke="#5fa05a" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
        <!-- Folha grande direita -->
        <path d="M152 120 C178 100 212 95 218 68 C224 41 198 30 168 56 C152 70 150 100 152 120Z" fill="#6AAB65" opacity="0.9"/>
        <path d="M152 120 C165 95 185 82 202 64" stroke="#4d8e49" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
        <!-- Folha pequena topo -->
        <path d="M138 60 C120 44 108 20 118 8 C128 -4 148 14 152 38 C154 50 144 58 138 60Z" fill="#7EB87A" opacity="0.85"/>
        <path d="M138 60 C132 44 126 28 120 12" stroke="#5fa05a" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
        <!-- Folha extra -->
        <path d="M133 180 C108 168 86 162 82 142 C78 122 100 112 122 132 C132 142 134 166 133 180Z" fill="#8fc98b" opacity="0.7"/>
        <!-- Detalhes vaso -->
        <line x1="105" y1="258" x2="105" y2="308" stroke="#2a5c2c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="140" y1="258" x2="140" y2="308" stroke="#2a5c2c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="175" y1="258" x2="175" y2="308" stroke="#2a5c2c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <span class="hero-tagline">natureza que se renova</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MANIFESTO -->
<div class="manifesto">
  <p class="manifesto-quote">"Cada vaso Renovata é feito para <em>durar, viver</em> e ser devolvido à terra quando chegar a hora."</p>
  <span class="manifesto-sub">— propósito Renovata</span>
</div>

<!-- PRODUTOS -->
<section class="produtos" id="produtos">
  <div class="produtos-intro">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Coleção</p>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Vasos que contam histórias naturais</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Cada peça é pensada para integrar estética e responsabilidade. Materiais renováveis, formas orgânicas e acabamentos que envelhecem com beleza.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="produtos-grid">
    <!-- Produto 1 -->
    <div class="produto-card">
      <div class="produto-img produto-img-1">
        <svg width="120" height="160" viewBox="0 0 120 160" fill="none">
          <path d="M30 130 L20 60 Q20 50 30 50 L90 50 Q100 50 100 60 L90 130 Q88 140 60 140 Q32 140 30 130Z" fill="#2D4A2F" opacity="0.2"/>
          <path d="M35 130 L25 62 Q25 56 35 56 L85 56 Q95 56 95 62 L85 130 Q83 138 60 138 Q37 138 35 130Z" fill="#2D4A2F" opacity="0.4"/>
          <rect x="20" y="46" width="80" height="12" rx="3" fill="#2D4A2F" opacity="0.3"/>
          <path d="M60 50 C60 30 50 15 55 5 C60 -5 70 10 65 25 C63 35 60 45 60 50Z" fill="#7EB87A"/>
          <path d="M60 50 C60 30 48 20 46 12 C44 4 56 0 60 14 C62 24 60 40 60 50Z" fill="#6AAB65" opacity="0.8"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="produto-info">
        <p class="produto-tag">Bambu Natural</p>
        <h3 class="produto-nome">Vaso Sereno</h3>
        <p class="produto-desc">Fibra de bambu prensada, 100% biodegradável. Ideal para plantas de interior.</p>
        <div class="produto-footer">
          <span class="produto-preco">R$ 89</span>
          <a href="#contato" class="produto-btn">+</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Produto 2 -->
    <div class="produto-card">
